scene.message:
Female Student: Eee, look,{nl}
look~ This skirt is so{nl}
cheap~{color:3}♥{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: Ah... cute clothes...{nl}
ah... too expensive after{nl}
all...{waitkey}{ret}

Himeno: U-um... do you think{nl}
they'd... buy my uniform off{nl}
me?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Yuko Himeno{nl}
Maki's friend. An admirable{nl}
girl working a job for her{nl}
family's sake.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: It's all practical{nl}
clothing. More like armor{nl}
than clothes.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Is this shopkeeper{nl}
from Demon Mountain too, like{nl}
the weapon seller across the{nl}
way?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: How many times this{nl}
shop's armor has saved our{nl}
lives.{waitkey}{clearbox}Even overcharged a bit, I{nl}
can't complain.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey, what's with{nl}
this shop, selling wild{nl}
clothes at school?{waitkey}{clearbox}Ah well, the dress code{nl}
hardly matters now anyway.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Even after school's{nl}
back to normal, I'll wear{nl}
these clothes to class.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: If we died, business{nl}
would dry up for them.{waitkey}{clearbox}Sure enough, they've stocked{nl}
some fine things.{waitkey}{ret}
